payload.text:
To update the website with the complete list of branches and emphasize West Mambalam as the primary flagship location, I will update the data constants, the location page layout, and the footer.

# Updated files:

## types.ts

Added `rating` and `notes` fields to the `Branch` interface to support the additional details provided.

<change>
<file>types.ts</file>
<description>Add rating and notes fields to Branch interface to support detailed branch info</description>
<content><![CDATA[
